      • createToken

        public static Task<jp.pay.android.model.Token> createToken(PayjpTokenService $this,
                                                           java.lang.String number,
                                                           java.lang.String cvc,
                                                           java.lang.String expMonth,
                                                           java.lang.String expYear,
                                                           java.lang.String name,
                                                           TenantId tenantId)

        Create token from card information.

        パラメータ:
        $this - card number
        number - card cvc
        cvc - card expiration month (zero-padding 2 digits e.g. January -> 01)
        expMonth - card expiration year (4 digits e.g. 2020 -> 2020)
        expYear - card holder name
        name - tenant id (only for platform)
        tenantId - tenant id (only for platform)
        戻り値:
        task to create token.
